            "Title":"View",
            "Project":"DSA/GNA ",
            "Summary":"<div class=\"ExternalClass27F57CDC777545F2B8CEE4742F040F99\"><p><span style=\"font-size&#58;11pt;font-family&#58;arial, sans-serif;color&#58;black;\">We personally believe that this award is coming little late from our end. &#160;Awards and accolades are mostly supported by particular project\u2019s success or visibility. &#160;But sheer excellence should deserve a reward no matter what. </span></p>\n<p></p><div style=\"margin&#58;0in 0in 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size&#58;11pt;font-family&#58;arial, sans-serif;color&#58;black;\">&#160;Priyadarshan is a perfect example of this and we would like to nominate him for his excellent work and exceptional capabilities. Over the past years, Priyadarshan contributed significantly being a strong and dependable GNA team player.&#160; &#160;He is also a \u2018go-to\u2019 person for everyone in the team. </span></div>\n<div style=\"margin&#58;0in 0in 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size&#58;11pt;font-family&#58;arial, sans-serif;color&#58;black;\">&#160;What we like about Priyadarshan is ability to help everyone in all situations. He never hesitates to perform well organized research for any questions he or others may have. Besides his involvement in complex GNA requests, Merchants Module, his involvement in variety of add-on projects like HIM is commendable.</span></div>\n<div style=\"margin&#58;0in 0in 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size&#58;11pt;font-family&#58;arial, sans-serif;color&#58;black;\">&#160;Thanks Priyadarshan for the superiority that you bring to the table thru your deliverable and also many thanks for being a backbone of GNA !</span></div>\n<div style=\"margin&#58;0in 0in 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size&#58;11pt;font-family&#58;arial, sans-serif;color&#58;black;\">&#160;Great job over the years and keep the momentum going ! </span></div>\n<div style=\"margin&#58;0in 0in 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size&#58;11pt;font-family&#58;arial, sans-serif;\">&#160;</span></div>\n<p></p></div>"
