            "Title":"View",
            "Project":"Cognos SDK Metadata Application",
            "Summary":"<div class=\"ExternalClass1A77AD11B30D4DA9883B4364695F7A01\"><p>\u200b<span style=\"font-family&#58;arial, sans-serif;\">IBM Cognos Business Intelligence &#160;provides a toolset for <a title=\"Report\" href=\"http&#58;//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Report#Enterprise.2FClient_reporting\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"text-decoration&#58;none;color&#58;windowtext;\">reporting</span></a>, <a title=\"Analytics\" href=\"http&#58;//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Analytics\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"text-decoration&#58;none;color&#58;windowtext;\">analysis</span></a>, <a title=\"Balanced scorecard\" href=\"http&#58;//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Balanced_scorecard\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"text-decoration&#58;none;color&#58;windowtext;\">score carding</span></a>, and monitoring of events and metrics.</span></p>\n<p></p><div style=\"margin&#58;0in 0in 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family&#58;arial, sans-serif;\">Being user-friendly it helps in developing various reports for different business areas. As a result, multiple reports are created and stored on Cognos content store.</span></div>\n<div style=\"margin&#58;0in 0in 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family&#58;arial, sans-serif;\">However, when it comes to maintenance part, it becomes complicated. Cognos is not very helpful when you want to find the information about the packages or reports being modified, assigned roles and groups to the business users. There are no open source, cost effective third party solutions available in the market. &#160;To achieve this, Discover Cognos team opted for third party tool known as \u2018 BSP Metamanager\u2019. &#160;With only single license, onsite team became dependent on Offshore to provide the output whenever required. </span></div><p></p>\n<div style=\"margin&#58;0in 0in 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family&#58;arial, sans-serif;\">Sanket with its out of box thinking came up with an idea to develop an application which would replace this third party tool \u2018BSP Metamanager\u2019. With no prior knowledge of Java coding, he had to learn the basics of &#160;the Java and implement it to develop this new \u2018Cognos Metadata application\u2018.&#160; Soon, Sanket mastered the language and completed complex coding and testing of Java programs which could directly fetch the information from Cognos content store.&#160;&#160;</span></div>\n<div style=\"margin&#58;0in 0in 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family&#58;arial, sans-serif;\"></span><span style=\"font-family&#58;arial, sans-serif;\">From this new application DFS will have annual saving of <b>$10,000 every year</b>. Onsite manager \u2018John Mckeown\u2019 greatly appreciated the efforts put in to develop this new application.</span></div>\n<div style=\"margin&#58;0in 0in 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family&#58;arial, sans-serif;\"></span><span style=\"font-family&#58;arial, sans-serif;\"></span>&#160;</div>\n<div style=\"margin&#58;0in 0in 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family&#58;arial, sans-serif;\">The innovative thinking followed by dedicated and focused implementation contributed to the success of this new application. From time and again Sanket has delivered exceptional commitment, proactive approach on every project/task given to him.</span></div>\n<div style=\"margin&#58;0in 0in 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family&#58;arial, sans-serif;\"></span>&#160;</div>\n<div style=\"margin&#58;0in 0in 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family&#58;arial, sans-serif;\"></span><span style=\"font-family&#58;arial, sans-serif;\">Great work Sanket! We are proud of you. ..Keep it up.</span></div>\n<p></p><div style=\"margin&#58;0in 0in 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family&#58;arial, sans-serif;\">&#160;</span></div>\n<p></p></div>"
